**NEW PHOTOS**
Get out of the CITY!!
Bring your Creativity, Alot of Potential. Conveniently Located right off 23rd Near Downtown Choctaw, and Downtown Harrah.
This is a Spacious 4 bedroom House, 2 and a HALF bath room, with 2 living areas, ON a .49 acre lot. 
including a large den, with a true Master Suite off the Den.
And only one neighbor to the East.

Also Has a 20X40 shop; and storm shelter
NEW ROOF  8/2023
NEW FLOORING throughout house, and renovated Master BED and MASTER BATH
